overview: This is history in the making. Bonnie Rotten will soon be retiring, and this is Rocco Siffredi's last film. The queen of squirt and Italy's finest go toe to toe!  "'Bonnie vs. Rocco' is probably my biggest movie of 2015 and one of my last big features before I retire from performing. Working with Bonnie is absolutely incredible, she is one of the few porn stars to leave a mark on me in my whole career; she's unpredictable and you never know what's going to happen when she's on set.
title: Bonnie Vs Rocco
